  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>This page contains the errata for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i>.\n</p>\n<table style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;border:3px solid #cfbd94; -moz-border-radius: 10px; -webkit-border-radius: 10px; border-radius:10px; float:right;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;color:#000\">\n<table class=\"infoboxinfobox-body\" cellspacing=\"5\" style=\"&quot;width:23em;\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"sidebar-above\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; text-align:center;border:0\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Errata\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Errata\"><i>A Song of Ice and Fire</i> Errata</a></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"\" style=\"text-align:center; border:0; background: #e9dac1; font-size:90%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series\" title=\"Errata of main series\">Main series</a></th></tr><tr class=\"\"><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"\" style=\"text-align:center; border:0; font-size:85%\"> <i><a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series#A_Game_of_Thrones_Errata\" title=\"Errata of main series\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (<a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series#A_Game_of_Thrones_Appendix\" title=\"Errata of main series\">Appendix</a>)<br /><i><a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series#A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"Errata of main series\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (<a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series#A_Clash_of_Kings_Appendix\" title=\"Errata of main series\">Appendix</a>)<br /><i><a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series#A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"Errata of main series\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (<a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series#A_Storm_of_Swords_Appendix\" title=\"Errata of main series\">Appendix</a>)<br /><i><a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_main_series#A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"Errata of main series\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (<a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_mai